1
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:39,880
Okay, I got it.

2
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:37,840
Spirit, return. Spirit, return.

3
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,080
Liu Liu.

4
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,640
Put the knife down.

5
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:49,240
Your illness can be cured.

6
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:52,080
You don't need to punish yourself like this.

7
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,680
You have to trust Master.

8
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,680
If you go through with this,

9
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,200
you'll fall completely into darkness.

10
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,760
Liu Liu.

11
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,920
Master knows

12
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,760
you have an obsession with Yaoyao's death.

13
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,800
But that's no reason to punish yourself

14
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,080
or to hurt others.

15
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,400
Liu Liu.

16
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,040
Are you listening?

17
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,520
Liu Liu.

18
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:27,560
Let the spirit's blood show the way,

19
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:30,600
guiding you onto the path to heaven.

20
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:34,560
Only when vengeance is served

21
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:37,560
can the spirit rest in peace.

22
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,480
Old Witch!

23
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,760
This is nothing but black magic.

24
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,360
Let me tell you both,

25
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,720
killing someone has legal consequences.

26
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,400
Desecrating a spirit

27
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:52,280
will bring retribution!

28
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,160
Boss.

29
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,160
What are you doing?

30
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,240
Liu Liu.

31
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,480
Liu Liu.

32
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,120
Wake up, Liu Liu!

33
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,720
So you still think

34
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,360
they're worth saving, huh?

35
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,640
Brother.

36
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,280
You're right.

37
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,760
This world is too complicated.

38
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,120
So I don't want any distractions.

39
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,600
Stay back!

40
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,560
I don't mind dying with him.

41
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,080
All of you, stay back!

42
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,480
Lin You!

43
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,840
Lin You, don't do anything rash!

44
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:10,640
Liu Liu.

45
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:13,960
Liu Liu.

46
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,520
Wake up, Liu Liu.

47
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:07,080
Wake up, Liu Liu!

48
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,160
Xu Liu Liu!

49
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,920
At a time like this,

50
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,720
what are you still hesitating for?

51
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,440
I can't.

52
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,920
I can't kill Master.

53
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,640
What about Qi Xiaoyu, then?

54
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,520
Don't tell me

55
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,680
you don't want to avenge Yaoyao anymore?

56
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,080
Lin You said

57
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:37,680
Qi Xiaoyu

58
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:40,120
has already been punished by the law.

59
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,080
And what about you?

60
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,200
If they don't die,

61
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,040
can you ever forgive yourself?

62
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,160
If it weren't for you,

63
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:50,080
Yaoyao would never have died.

64
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:51,880
Others may not know,

65
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,440
but don't you know, Xu Liu Liu?

66
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,720
Yes.

67
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:02,200
No one ever wanted revenge.

68
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,000
It was always my fault.

69
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,240
I'm the one who deserves to die.

70
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,840
I'm the one who deserves to die.

71
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,800
That's right.

72
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,640
Kill them,

73
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,160
or kill yourself.

74
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,600
Either way, you'll find release.

75
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,520
How can it be you?

76
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:42,880
Yaoyao.

77
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,440
Yaoyao,

78
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,440
I'm sorry.

79
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,840
It's all my fault.

80
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,200
If only back then,

81
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,800
I hadn't insisted on going to that birthday party.

82
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,520
If I had refused them,

83
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,200
you wouldn't have died.

84
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:10,040
I knew you'd take all the blame

85
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,480
onto your own shoulders.

86
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,320
But, Liu Liu,

87
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,680
that really wasn't your fault.

88
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,160
Blame me.

89
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,000
It's my fault.

90
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:28,000
Back then,

91
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:30,520
if I had only insisted a little more

92
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,960
on my own decision,

93
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,720
you wouldn't have died.

94
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,880
That's not true, Liu Liu.

95
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,360
Master was right.

96
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,400
People

97
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,880
are always swayed by their own thoughts,

98
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,320
whether good ones

99
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,640
or bad ones.

100
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,800
The one who's been affecting you all along

101
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:54,960
has been you yourself.

102
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:59,440
But that's not how it really is.

103
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,040
You just couldn't accept

104
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,960
the fact that your best friend

105
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,760
died right in front of you.

106
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:11,840
I...

107
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:15,240
I just couldn't bear to lose you.

108
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,320
I couldn't bear to lose you.

109
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,160
That's right.

110
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,760
And that's exactly why

111
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,400
I haven't been able to leave in peace.

112
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,360
So,

113
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,720
the best way to set me free

114
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,760
isn't to punish anyone.

115
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,080
It's for you, Liu Liu,

116
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,880
to learn to let me go.

117
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:50,800
Look,

118
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,600
even in a life without me,

119
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,440
you can still live well.

120
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,560
Isn't that right?

121
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,720
No.

122
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,560
That's not true, Yaoyao.

123
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,280
That's not true, Yaoyao.

124
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:11,080
That's not true, Yaoyao.

125
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,600
It's okay.

126
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,760
You've already done so, so well.

127
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,960
Just think about it.

128
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,240
At Daji,

129
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,920
every person you've met,

130
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,920
every situation,

131
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,880
whether it was Yiyi,

132
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,880
or Grandma Sun,

133
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:35,960
or Lu Xing,

134
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,640
all those things you thought

135
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,560
you couldn't handle on your own,

136
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:43,520
in the end, didn't you solve them all yourself?

137
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,480
It was me.

138
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,120
It was you.

139
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,640
Of course,

140
00:10:58,280 --> 00:10:59,480
if you insist on saying

141
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:01,680
you solved them in my name,

142
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:03,960
I'll accept that too.

143
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,440
Liu Liu.

144
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,160
Your future will

145
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,560
definitely get better and better.

146
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:33,560
Because

147
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,680
you have a family you can rely on.

148
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:40,000
You have someone who would,

149
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,320
to protect you,

150
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,360
give up his own life.

151
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,720
He promised me he'd take good care of you.

152
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,760
If he can't do that,

153
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,800
I'll take him away with me.

154
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:03,720
All right.

155
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,200
Goodbye,

156
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:17,080
my dear Liu Liu.

157
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,760
I hope from now on

158
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,600
you can be stronger

159
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,600
and a little braver.

160
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,520
This is the last time I'll protect you.

161
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,280
Goodbye.

162
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:48,840
Yaoyao!

163
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,800
No!

164
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,120
Don't go!

165
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:58,520
Please don't leave!

166
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,320
Yaoyao!

167
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,280
Don't go!

168
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:09,240
Yaoyao!

169
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:11,760
Yaoyao!

170
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:22,640
Yaoyao, Yaoyao!

171
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,400
Lin You.

172
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,280
I'm sorry.

173
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,920
I made you all worry.

174
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:07,720
I'm sorry.

175
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,520
You saw her.

176
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,360
Save him first.

177
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:24,360
Master.

178
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,960
Master, I'm sorry.

179
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,960
It's okay, it's okay.

180
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,360
Careful.

181
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:31,360
Lin You.

182
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:33,760
Don't make things difficult for us.

183
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:34,680
Right.

184
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:35,800
Move aside!

185
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:38,160
Move aside, Lin You!

186
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,720
Come on, Liu Liu.

187
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,000
Lin You.

188
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,120
Let's go.

189
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,760
Lin You.

190
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:06,440
Let's go.

191
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:10,800
Lin You.

192
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,840
You're just leaving like this?

193
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:53,920
Lin You.
